<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> If, in order to vote or to stand as candidates, nationals of the Member State of residence must have spent a certain minimum period as a resident in the territory of that State, voters and persons entitled to stand as candidates within the scope of Article 3 shall be deemed to have fulfilled that condition where they have resided for an equivalent period in other Member States. </inglise>
