<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Member State of residence shall inform the person concerned in good time of the action taken on his application for entry on the electoral roll or of the decision concerning the admissibility of his application to stand as a candidate. </inglise>
